data.description: Welcome to this inviting home, just minutes from downtown Woodinville. Updated w/new carpet, fresh paint throughout. Spacious living room w/soaring vaulted ceilings & granite fireplace. Updated kitchen w/cherry cabinets, granite countertops, SS appliances & a walk-in pantry. The large family room is perfect for entertainment or relaxation. There’s no shortage of storage space throughout the home. The primary bedroom is a true retreat, complete w/a sitting room loft & a private ensuite bath. Step outside onto the expansive deck, perfect for outdoor dining & entertaining. The fully fenced yard provides privacy & security. With restaurants, shops & wineries nearby, this home offers both comfort & convenience for a vibrant lifestyle.
